      Disjoint c5 [0, 4, 5, 6, 7]: mult 0->1 (delta=1)
    Lost c3 [1, 5, 7] (cap S = 2):
      Disjoint c5 [0, 2, 3, 4, 6]: mult 0->1 (delta=1)
    Gained c3 [1, 2, 7] (cap S = 2):
      Disjoint c5 [0, 3, 4, 5, 6]: mult 1->0 (delta=-1)
    Gained c3 [1, 3, 5] (cap S = 2):
      Disjoint c5 [0, 2, 4, 6, 7]: mult 1->0 (delta=-1)

  Example 3 (dH=-2):
