      Disjoint c5 [1, 3, 4, 5, 6]: mult 1->3 (delta=2)
    Lost c3 [3, 5, 7] (cap S = 2):
      Disjoint c5 [0, 1, 2, 4, 6]: mult 1->3 (delta=2)
    Gained c3 [0, 5, 7] (cap S = 2):
      Disjoint c5 [1, 2, 3, 4, 6]: mult 3->1 (delta=-2)
    Gained c3 [2, 3, 7] (cap S = 2):
      Disjoint c5 [0, 1, 4, 5, 6]: mult 3->1 (delta=-2)

  Example 4 (dH=2):
